StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.name: [GetMapsSectorZipByRecrui.ngPersonId]
StoredProcedureSqlServerv2k5.body:
@Recrui.ngPersonId uniqueidentifier AS BEGIN
SET TRANSACTION ISOLATION LEVEL READ UNCOMMITTED
SELECT MSZ.SectorZipId, MSZ.SectorID, MSZ.ZIP, MSZ.LastUpdateUserId FROM USMC.MapsSectorZip MSZ INNER JOIN USMC.MapsSectorRecruiter MSR ON MSR.SectorID=MSZ.SectorID WHERE MSR.Recrui.ngPersonId=@Recrui.ngPersonId
END
